Hlaudi Motsoeneng Picture: Simphiwe Nkwali Axed SABC boss Hlaudi Motsoeneng is positive about his future and insists that, despite the furore around his employment at the public broadcaster, South Africans are still going to see me . He was speaking at a church service held to pray for him in Mpumalanga on Sunday, the Sowetan reported. The dismissal of Hlaudi is the beginning of Hlaudi. I hold my future in my hands. The SABC is not the end of the world Motsoeneng said. He was fired by the interim SABC board after a prolonged disciplinary hearing. Share on Facebook Share Share on Twitter Tweet Share on Google Plus Share